n\n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group lg-legal-counsel has-background has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-c3cfcf2e wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"border-radius:8px;border-left-color:#0052ab;border-left-width:4px;background-color:#f2f7fb;margin-top:40px;padding-top:30px;padding-right:30px;padding-bottom:30px;padding-left:30px\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-color\" style=\"color:#023e8a;font-size:clamp(15.747px, 0.984rem + ((1vw - 3.2px) * 0.86), 24px);font-style:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.5px;text-transform:uppercase\">Legal Counsel</h2>\n\n\n<p><strong>Corporate Counsel:</strong> Miller Thomson LLP, 40 King Street West, Suite 5800, Toronto, Ontario M5H 3S1</p>\n<p><strong>Securities Counsel:</strong> Fasken Martineau DuMoulin LLP, 1200-600 Bay Street, Toronto, Ontario M5H 2R7</p>\n<p><strong>IP &amp; Technology Counsel:</strong> Gowling WLG, 1600-160 Elgin Street, Ottawa, Ontario K1P 1C3</p></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group lgp-pattern-starter lgp-pattern-starter-v1 has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Pattern Starter (Editor Only)</h4>\n<p>Duplicate one of the blocks below, then edit text/images. This starter is hidden on the live frontend.</p>\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group lgp-section lgp-hero-shell has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\"><figure style=\"aspect-ratio:16/6;\" class=\"wp-block-post-featured-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1600\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://loungenie.com/staging/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/hero-investor-relations.png\" class=\"attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;\" srcset=\"https://loungenie.com/staging/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/hero-investor-relations.png 1600w, https://loungenie.com/staging/wp-